description: Lists the history of SPICE ingestions for a dataset.

parameters.name: DataSetId
parameters.description: The ID of the dataset used in the ingestion.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID.

nested_items.name: Ingestions
nested_items.description: A list of the ingestions.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource.

nested_items.name: IngestionId
nested_items.description: Ingestion ID.

nested_items.name: IngestionStatus
nested_items.description: Ingestion status.

nested_items.name: ErrorInfo
nested_items.description: Error information for this ingestion.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: Error type.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: Error message.

nested_items.name: RowsIngested
nested_items.description: The number of rows that were ingested.

nested_items.name: RowsDropped
nested_items.description: The number of rows that were not ingested.

nested_items.name: TotalRowsInDataset
nested_items.description: The total number of rows in the dataset.

nested_items.name: QueueInfo
nested_items.description: Information about a queued dataset SPICE ingestion.

nested_items.name: WaitingOnIngestion
nested_items.description: The ID of the queued ingestion.

nested_items.name: QueuedIngestion
nested_items.description: The ID of the ongoing ingestion. The queued ingestion is waiting for the ongoing ingestion to complete.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that this ingestion started.

nested_items.name: IngestionTimeInSeconds
nested_items.description: The time that this ingestion took, measured in seconds.

nested_items.name: IngestionSizeInBytes
nested_items.description: The size of the data ingested, in bytes.

nested_items.name: RequestSource
nested_items.description: Event source for this ingestion.

nested_items.name: RequestType
nested_items.description: Type of this ingestion.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
